Quota allocation
The quantity set for the annual tariff quota period referred to in Annex I, part B, shall be allocated in four tariff subperiods as follows:
(a) 25 % from 1 July to 30 September;
(b) 25 % from 1 October to 31 December;
(c) 25 % from 1 January to 31 March;
(d) 25 % from 1 April to 30 June.
